---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support SQLTemple"
  description="Ways to contribute, donate, and help SQLTemple grow."
>
  <section class="container section space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Support SQLTemple</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-lg max-w-3xl">
      SQLTemple is an independent project. Here are lightweight ways to help:
      contribute code, share feedback, or support hosting costs in the future.
    </p>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface-2 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contribute</h3>
        <p class="text-muted mb-3">
          Open issues, tackle bugs, or add docs. Good first issues are tagged in
          GitHub.
        </p>
        <a
          class="text-accent"
          href="https://github.com/vicotrbb/sqltemple/issues"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer">View issues →</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface-2 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Feedback</h3>
        <p class="text-muted mb-3">
          Request features or share what slows you down. It shapes the roadmap.
        </p>
        <a class="text-accent" href="mailto:victorbona+sqltemple@hotmail.com"
          >Email maintainer →</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface-2 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Donate (soon)</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          We will add donation links to help the continue development of
          SQLTemple. Stay tuned.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
